  "title": "Insurance Specialist #76246",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Towing Service</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Insurance Specialist</strong></li><li>Working Location: Redhill</li><li>Working Hours: Monday – Friday (8am to 6pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary up to $3300 + AWS + Incentive</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Handle counter, email, and phone enquiries for general insurance products.</li><li>Provide insurance quotations and process applications, renewals, extensions, cancellations, and issue related documents.</li><li>Support customers in both spoken and written communication.</li><li>Make telemarketing calls and assist with marketing campaigns when needed.</li><li>Cross-sell various general insurance products to customers.</li><li>Perform daily opening and closing procedures, including transaction and payment terminal checks.</li><li>Assist the Operations Executive with daily tasks and ad-hoc assignments.</li><li>Complete required training hours and follow all regulatory guidelines.</li><li>Carry out other tasks assigned by supervisors as needed.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>At least 3 GCE ‘O’ Level credit passes or Basic Competency Examination (BCE) Certificate.</li><li>Certificate in General Insurance (CGI), BCP & PGI, or ComGI is an advantage.</li><li>Minimum 1 year of relevant experience preferred.</li><li>Courteous, helpful, and proactive attitude.</li><li>Passion for delivering excellent customer service.</li><li>Experienced and mature candidates in the insurance sector are welcome.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#76246 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
